          <h2 class="page-header">
            <em class="vote-name">McDonalds Spring Promotion</em>
          </h2>
          <h3>
            <span>Candidate - </span>XXXXXX</span>
          </h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Author - </strong>
            <span>Ukey</span>
          </p>
          <p><strong>Introduction</strong></p>
<pre>McDonald’s will open franchises to individuals in Central and West China such as Sichuan Province and Chongqing, which has been confirmed by McDonald’s (China).</pre>
          <form action="" >
            <label for="inputScore">Score:</label>
            <input type="number" name="inputScore" val="0" max="10" min="0">
            <label for="inputComment">Comment:</label>
            <label for=""><textarea name="inputComment" id="" cols="30" rows="5" class="vote-comment"></textarea></label>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
            <span class="timer alert alert-success">Left:<span>30</span>s</span>
          </form>
        </div>
      </section>
    </article>
  </body>
